cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with authorship verification, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a machine learning approach using neural networks, which makes it relevant to categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with text comparison, which is related to information retrieval, making cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a likely category. Finally, the paper deals with social media texts, which could make it relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
